# Fumadocs Patterns

## Source API (`lib/source.ts`)

```typescript
import { source } from '@/lib/source';
source.getPage(slugs);      // get single page
source.getPageTree();        // sidebar tree
source.generateParams();     // static params
```

## Doc page template (`app/docs/[[...slug]]/page.tsx`)

Uses `DocsPage`, `DocsTitle`, `DocsDescription`, `DocsBody` from `fumadocs-ui`.
MDX body: `page.data.body`. TOC: `page.data.toc`.
Relative links via `createRelativeLink(source, page)`.

## Layouts

- Root: `RootProvider` from `fumadocs-ui`, `lang="ja"`
- Docs: `DocsLayout` with `source.getPageTree()`

## Types

- `PageProps<'/docs/[[...slug]]'>`, `LayoutProps<'/docs'>` — Next.js 16 generated types
- `InferPageType<typeof source>` — Fumadocs page type

## Generated files

`.source/` dir is auto-generated by `fumadocs-mdx`. Gitignored. Regenerate with `pnpm postinstall`.
